PQdUSyBL8T8.title: THENX EURO TOUR - LISBON, PORTUGAL | 2018 Ep.1
PQdUSyBL8T8.description:
Lisbon, Portugal was unreal. This was the city of art.
Every where you look, these walls tell a story that goes back hundreds of years.
This tour was our first tour ever for the team.We were to land in Lisbon for a workshop,
Drive to Madrid for a meet n greet, Fly to Zürich for a workshop, and finish in London for our final workshop of the tour. And we were to do all that, in just ten days.
From the plane we headed straight to the gym with no delay we were hitting the ground running straight into our first workshop into the heart of Lisbon at the RawLX gym ...
Stay tuned Next Thursday for Ep. 2 Madrid Spain
